      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, making it the perfect choice for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for a high-potential fixer-upper. While it needs some significant TLC to get back to its prime, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a quality model at a fraction of the cost!",
